  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You coat your mind in a chakra designed to be malleable and reflect change well. When you would gain a mental or sensory condition you can bounce it back to any hostile creature within range.</p><p>Target creature must make an Intelligence saving throw.</p><p>Success: Affected creature is able to resist this jutsu's effects.</p><p>Failure: Affected creature gains whatever Mental or Sensory conditions you would gain as if they failed their own saving throw.</p><p>Critical Failure: Affected creature suffers the same effects of a Failure, and also cannot remove the condition themselves and instead must spend an action to remake this jutsu's saving throw to end them.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
